        <h2>
            中国化的日本的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 28 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5989225">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5989225/" class="title-link">中国化的日本</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5989225"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/31678134/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u31678134-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/31678134/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">King</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-05-24"
      class="main-meta">2013-05-24 17:07:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5989225_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    　此书相当精彩。许多青年人也许会以为这是一本近似《货币战争》之类奇思怪想的书籍，当然写中国好还是令人高兴的。说实话我开始时也有点这种心思，至多认为是一本有点历史随笔杂文性质的书籍，真没想到是一部即通俗又严肃的历史论著。 　　要让许多青年人失望了，此书的中国...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5989225/#comments">(16回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">42有用 / 5没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5989225_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5989225_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
